Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:29.66,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}彷徨於無盡的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.53,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}身陷於此
