Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:43.17,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今宵明月邀我為伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.81,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便仍道不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.97,SAOOP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心中早已呐喊無數
